Class CTPServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rsna.servlets.Servlet
      • org.rsna.ctp.servlets.CTPServlet
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DBVerifierServlet, DicomAnonymizerServlet, IDMapServlet, LookupServlet, LookupTableCheckerServlet, ObjectTrackerServlet, QuarantineServlet, ScriptServlet, SummaryServlet

    public class CTPServlet
extends org.rsna.servlets.Servlet
    The CTPServlet servlet. This servlet is a framework for CTP servlets that access data from PipelineStages using the p and s query parameters to identify the stage.
